                            </p>
                            <p class="pickup-detail__date en">
                                2024.01.20
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="">
                        <div class="pickup-thumb">
                            <img src="<%= rootURL %>/assets/img/dummy/dummy_3.jpg" alt="">
